text: Lev Kokorin was a water polo player from Soviet Union. Lev competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics. He was born on 19 August 1918 and died on 1 February 1989.Lev Kokorin == References == Category:1918 births Category:1989 deaths Category:Olympians for the Soviet Union Category:Water polo players
title: Lev Kokorin
